Package net.sf.jclec.mo.algorithm

Generic algorithm definition package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MOECAlgorithm
    An abstract algorithm to solve multi-objective problems.
    MOEPAlgorithm
    Multi-objective Evolutionary Programming (EP) Algorithm.
    MOESAlgorithm
    Multi-objective Evolution Strategy (ES) Algorithm.
    MOGeneticAlgorithm
    Multi-objective Genetic Algorithm (GA).
    MOGPAlgorithm
    Multi-objective Genetic Programming (GP) Algorithm.
    MOOnlyRecombinatorAlgorithm
    This class implements a genetic algorithm in which only recombination is performed.
    MOPSOAlgorithm
    A generic PSO algorithm to solve multi-objective problems.
